Package org.opengis.cite.kml2.c3 Description

Conformance level 3 (CL3) includes the tests for CL2 and adds tests to check optional constraints that are essentially informative in nature. These tests are intended to flag the use of deprecated elements or to encourage alignment with existing (non-normative) geomatics standards or conventions.
See Also:
"OGC 14-068r2: OGC KML 2.3 - Abstract Test Suite", "OGC-07-134r2: OGC KML 2.2 - Abstract Test Suite"
